h1. Socrata-node

Uses our existing dataset model from the frontend codebase to enable powerful API scripting via Node.js.

h2. Requirements

Runs on Node.js 0.4.0 and above.

h2. Dependencies

h3. Running directly/via REPL

Install the following npm packages:
* underscore
* restler
* mime

Run @make@ to build the relevant files.

h3. Building local software

Run @make@ to build the relevant files.

Run @npm link@ in this directory to link the package to the global npm context for development.

Go to the directory that contains your code.

Run @npm link socrata@ to link the package from global to that directory.
